{"tid":2440134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【內地大量貓隻被偷盜至江門市場待宰殺】 【貓販冷血反問：貓不用來吃，用來幹嘛？】","createTime":"2021-03-09T17:53:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T00:49:03.000Z","uid":49004,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"12b734e172b30ad25f769945496d437ed2357605","tid":2440134,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T17:53:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/videos/708702506491271/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkcnews%2Fvideos%2F708702506491271%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=3a3adcf1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/videos/708702506491271/</a><br />\n有愛貓的義工揭發近日有大量貓咪被盜，並運至江門禽畜交易市場待宰殺。大量義工趕到現場並報警，市監局已封鎖貓販的店舖，並將貓咪轉移到其他安置點。但有救貓義工指，市監局並未妥善照顧貓咪，安置點環境很差，貓咪間經常發生打鬥，希望當局盡快為貓咪完成健康檢查，讓他們可以妥善安置。<br />\n<br />\n在周六（6日），上海一隻叫「黃點點」的流浪貓失蹤，經常餵飼黃點點的義工跟隨牠身上的GPS定位，發現牠可能被捉走偷運走。她由上海一直開車追下去南方，最後發現黃點點被帶到去廣東江門的禽畜交易市場。<br />\n<br />\n在這個禽畜交易市場中，有大量貓被困起來等待屠宰。事件經網絡傳開後，大量義工趕到現場與商販談判，沒料貓販沒有絲毫歉意，更語出驚人：<br />\n「那些狗、貓是用來吃的！貓不是用來吃，用來幹甚麼？用來做你的爺嗎？還是給你做老公啊？」<br />\n<br />\n在江門禽畜交易市場中，有大量貓被困起來等待屠宰。網絡片段截圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.image.cx/q4Ye3.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.image.cx%2Fq4Ye3.webp&h=90df3ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現時內地只有深圳和珠海有立例禁食貓肉，因此買賣食用貓未必犯法，但偷盜貓咪則是犯法行為。義工於是報警，警察和市監局接報到場，封鎖貓販的店舖。當局指需要核查貓隻的來源，並將被扣查的貓咪轉移到其他安置點。<br />\n<br />\n有義工由周日（7日）晚上10點開始一直在安置點外看顧貓咪，雖然市監局職員指周一（8日）早上8點會來開門，但她等到早上11點都一直沒人來。「市監局根本不來人，讓我們能幹嘛呢？他們也不作為，也不干涉，也不給一個結果。甚麼部門都來過了，沒用的。現在甚麼都沒說，就是說把這些貓拿去安檢，檢查看有沒有甚麼病。」<br />\n<br />\n電話訪問途中，多次傳來貓咪打鬥叫囂的聲音。義工指現場環境很差，貓咪被密集地困在籠子中，不時都會打架：「牠們裡面死傷會很多的。這裡100隻貓，健康的肯定沒有5%。希望他們開門，給牠們吃的，盡快做治療，讓我們安置一下貓。從外圍拿點籠子、醫藥這些，為牠們保暖。」<br />\n<br />\n江門公安亦於網上呼籲報失的貓主盡快聯絡他們，又說他們致力打撃偷盜貓隻的違法行為，歡迎大眾積極舉報。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/38987/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F38987%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=12dfe25e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/38987/</a>"},{"pid":"160aa23d15bce2d9dbaee6008cc3fa226100b985","tid":2440134,"uid":35699,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T18:01:46.000Z","msg":"「那些狗、貓是用來吃的！貓不是用來吃，用來幹甚麼？用來做你的爺嗎？還是給你做老公啊？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8403ff1cad2903a4e7989627dc65489f72b0a6b","tid":2440134,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T18:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339ee327effcbf44c0dde0d1ff77e33dd2cc74e4","tid":2440134,"uid":54264,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T18:06:14.000Z","msg":"支那人真係癌細胞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048f3180f494354799cc3e6f6e2e272b7cf210a3","tid":2440134,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T18:08:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2441c42499c64526b6c2475e95665990f452265d","tid":2440134,"uid":323245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T18:11:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce16977742222e7efbc3f4fa11da4d8f9b027732","tid":2440134,"uid":52817,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T18:12:24.000Z","msg":"香港=貓"},{"pid":"cef41254aae52e2f1de092cfe91937c82f19e9e3","tid":2440134,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T18:14:02.000Z","msg":"動物撚協會訓緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb480f2c4e809b3254b89daf3131bbe3678abfc","tid":2440134,"uid":27530,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T18:14:36.000Z","msg":"拎流浪貓叫偷？<br />\n<br />\n獅子打獵算唔算偷？"},{"pid":"5be64e8afea997d4b822ab069226ccd1d1cad514","tid":2440134,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T18:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae62969684f61f2b4053534d501c4c3ff41f95ab","tid":2440134,"uid":254594,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"160aa23d15bce2d9dbaee6008cc3fa226100b985","tid":2440134,"uid":35699,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T18:01:46.000Z","msg":"「那些狗、貓是用來吃的！貓不是用來吃，用來幹甚麼？用來做你的爺嗎？還是給你做老公啊？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T18:16:19.000Z","msg":"「那些支那種是用來吃的！支那種不是用來吃，用來幹甚麼？用來做你的爺嗎？還是給你做老公啊？」<br />\n<br />\n百搭"},{"pid":"9fab5c2ddc51cd498fec0fbcedfa50a80088cad2","tid":2440134,"uid":299372,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T18:20:00.000Z","msg":"陶傑 ： 吃貓狗肉屬野蠻行為 沒有得辯駁<br />\n<br />\n廣西辦「狗肉節」，屠宰活狗，一片血腥。小狗關在籠子裏，看着同伴一隻隻被殘殺，眼色淒涼。<br />\n當地「領導」認為，食狗肉，是「文化習俗」。好了，又一次，萬試萬靈，文化習俗，理應「包容」。<br />\n問問香港的「文化學者」、「知識份子」叫這些人站出來，喝問，他們是否贊成「包容」屠宰貓狗，「包容」中國千百年吃狗肉的「文化」？<br />\n中國人喜歡辯駁：屠宰貓狗殘忍，不該吃狗肉，但「西方文明國家」都屠牛，宰羊，殺豬，一樣有牛排和香腸，為什麼要有「雙重標準」？<br />\n然而，吃牛肉與鵝肝均可，就是不可以宰食貓狗。這是「普世價值觀」很重要的條文──「普世價值觀」以西方文明為基礎，由西方的白人國家定規條：可以吃牛排、羊排、香腸，吃貓狗肉，即屬野蠻行為。這一點，沒有得辯駁，別無選擇，如果你想進入文明行列，只能跟着做。<br />\n正如國際足球的規矩，是英國人定的，其中的罰球，叫「十二碼」──首先，「碼」（Yard）這個量度單位是英國的，不錯，一米等於一點零九三碼，但十二碼就是十二碼，不叫十點九七米。即使足球在北京舉行，滿座的中國觀眾都是喊打喊殺的愛國毛左，罰球還是按照英國人定的，叫十二碼，中國人講政治，慣於亂搬龍門，但北京的足球，無論他多反英，鴉片戰爭有幾多仇恨，罰球還是乖乖的十二碼，不可以改為十三碼，或者九點一八米。<br />\n世界上許多常識，非常簡單，不要學舌辯駁。你去了伊朗，敢拿出一碟乳豬在清真寺外蹲下來吃嗎？你會跟四周的人說：請你「包容」我華夏的「吃豬肉文化」嗎？<br />\n他當然不包容，不但不包容，而且有一天，當拉登全球伊斯蘭的理想國建立了，全人類都禁食豬肉，殺豬食肉的，是野蠻的下等，正如西方國家今日鄙視屠宰貓狗的民族一樣。<br />\n如果是「習俗」，那麼不妨將廣西的狗肉市場圖片，發給西方國家的報刊、雜誌、西方的朋友和同事，然後叫你的白人鄰居去中國廣西旅遊，促進一下「文化交流」，讓他們也學學「包容」，增進了解，不是更好嗎？哈哈，廣傳出去吧。"},{"pid":"ba3a412957b35973e06307bb4c5c4c29bda240ad","tid":2440134,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"fcb480f2c4e809b3254b89daf3131bbe3678abfc","tid":2440134,"uid":27530,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T18:14:36.000Z","msg":"拎流浪貓叫偷？<br />\n<br />\n獅子打獵算唔算偷？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T21:52:50.000Z","msg":"獵殺獅子叫做盜獵，因為係非法<br />\n係中國捉流浪貓應該唔犯法，所以唔係偷，但係拎黎食好唔干淨lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPs 唔反對食狗肉但係我反對食貓肉，因為我鐘意貓"},{"pid":"ae834ab61afcc8db19a8d89f5a04c5925cd652da","tid":2440134,"uid":7206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T23:13:18.000Z","msg":"上海揸車黎廣東，咁似變形金剛北京揸車黎香港嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dddf9c741e4e7cb0dacd88f28883355c0260964f","tid":2440134,"uid":52459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T23:19:38.000Z","msg":"支那人唔殺晒佢哋，留係地球做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d629c4df47171cc8b352cee113221d7c35dc3a","tid":2440134,"uid":230530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T23:24:40.000Z","msg":"中國人值得雍有武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"6d9b386daaafa3ddbd2c2c848274318219a06a80","tid":2440134,"uid":62787,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T23:29:53.000Z","msg":"出得起錢自己老豆老母都可以比你食撚埋呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同啲畜生講道德"},{"pid":"ab5034cfa27e46d01f82d505673b5adde91519d5","tid":2440134,"uid":28913,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T23:37:14.000Z","msg":"呢d 係支那人天性, 不必隱藏, 比國際睇下仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27fe2142a855b42fc1a29734638f97cdde6bf20f","tid":2440134,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T23:43:24.000Z","msg":"連登有好多大廣東膠<br />\n佢地認為自己係同呢D賤畜同種<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99d557a381b8df3c741774a8a63122d59873cb4","tid":2440134,"uid":92633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T23:46:11.000Z","msg":"又係南方人"},{"pid":"8eba411c639b6807f85ced0491aa3b005330cf4f","tid":2440134,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T23:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/87/YellowTerror.jpg/220px-YellowTerror.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F8%2F87%2FYellowTerror.jpg%2F220px-YellowTerror.jpg&h=8c664ea2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e824279ada227d6b67aecd6c256134e5d8e4cd28","tid":2440134,"uid":23221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T00:34:17.000Z","msg":"部份支那人是地球癌細胞"},{"pid":"1c169c195d69e06626073bcbbed1f17caab3d731","tid":2440134,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T00:49:03.000Z","msg":"中囯人根本咁應該存在"}]}